        "\n",
        "**3. Protobuf conflicts**\n",
        "```\n",
        "# Remove system protobuf\n",
        "!apt-get remove libprotobuf-dev protobuf-compiler\n",
        "# Use vcpkg protobuf only\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "**4. Memory issues**\n",
        "```\n",
        "# Reduce parallel jobs\n",
        "!cmake --build . --config Release -j2\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "### Alternative: Use Docker Instead\n",
        "If build continues to fail, use the pre-built Docker image:\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "docker build -t rag-engine .\n",
        "docker run -p 8080:8080 rag-engine\n",
